# -- python3-requests-scitokens

Package: python3-requests-scitokens
Architecture: all
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${python3:Depends},
 python3-requests,
 python3-scitokens,
Description: SciTokens plugin for Requests
 requests-scitokens adds optional SciTokens authorisation support
 for the python3-requests HTTP library.
 .
 This package provides the Python 3 library.
